uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo
Root package for the HOBO framework, which contains all HOBO-specific exception classes, as well as providing the general overview documentation for the framework.

Provides the point-of-entry for applications using a direct HOBO model.

Point-of-entry for documentation of the MEKON and HOBO frameworks.

For a general overview of the HOBO framework and MEKON frameworks, and other related software see mekon-hobo project website.

For a code-level overview of the MEKON framework see uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.

For a code-level overview of the MEKON-OWL plug-ins see uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.

For a code-level overview of the HOBO framework see uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.
